## Specifying reference swapping
```
val swap : r1:ref int -> r2:ref int -> ST unit
    (requires (fun h' -> True ))
    (ensures (fun h' _ h ->
                sel h r1 = sel h' r2 /\ sel h r2 = sel h' r1))
let swap r1 r2 =
  let t = !r1 in
  r1 := !r2;
  r2 := t
```
Hand proof sketch in `code/03/SwapVerify.fst`


