## Preorder for Initializing and Freezing references ##

```
type rstate (a:Type) =
  | Empty : rstate a
  | Mutable : v:a -> rstate a
  | Frozen : v:a -> rstate a
```
~Fragment
```
let evolve (a:Type) = fun r1 r2 ->
  match r1, r2 with
  | Empty, Mutable _
  | Mutable _, Mutable _ -> True
  | Mutable v1, Frozen v2 -> v1 == v2
  | _, _ -> False
